    <h2 class="section-heading">How to Use PYQs Effectively</h2>

    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-3); margin-bottom:var(--space-6);">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);padding:var(--space-3) var(--space-4);background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-md);">
        <span style="font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">1️⃣</span>
        <div><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-text);margin:0 0 2px;">Topic-wise, not year-wise</p><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.5;margin:0;">Group by topic (all Polity PYQs together). Reveals which sub-topics UPSC returns to.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);padding:var(--space-3) var(--space-4);background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-md);">
        <span style="font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">2️⃣</span>
        <div><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-text);margin:0 0 2px;">Attempt before reading notes</p><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.5;margin:0;">Can't answer? Now you know what to focus on. Can? Move faster through that topic.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);padding:var(--space-3) var(--space-4);background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-md);">
        <span style="font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">3️⃣</span>
        <div><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-text);margin:0 0 2px;">Analyse wrong answers</p><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.5;margin:0;">Prelims: why was each option wrong? Mains: what dimensions did you miss? The gap = study guide.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);padding:var(--space-3) var(--space-4);background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-md);">
        <span style="font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">4️⃣</span>
        <div><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-text);margin:0 0 2px;">Track frequency</p><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.5;margin:0;">5+ times in 10 years = UPSC favourite. Invest disproportionate time there.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);padding:var(--space-3) var(--space-4);background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-md);">
        <span style="font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">5️⃣</span>
        <div><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-text);margin:0 0 2px;">Simulate exam conditions</p><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.5;margin:0;">100 Qs, 2 hours, no notes. Builds exam temperament — the #1 D-day factor.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);padding:var(--space-3) var(--space-4);background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-md);">
        <span style="font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">6️⃣</span>
        <div><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-text);margin:0 0 2px;">Revise with PYQs as flashcards</p><p style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.5;margin:0;">Can you answer each confidently? If not, revisit that topic. PYQs = ultimate revision checklist.</p></div>
      </div>
